Package: baseverse
Title: Modern Base-R Functions
Version: 0.1.4
Authors@R: 
    person(given = 'Yea-Hung', family = 'Chen', 
       email = 'yea-hung.chen@ucsf.edu', role = c('aut','cre'))
Description: Includes modern base-R functions, allowing for native piping. base_match() and base_when() mimic dplyr's case_match() and case_when(), but return a factor by default with levels ordered according to user input.
